The ultimate 100-point items often involve combining a filtered mundane liquid with a vial-extracted magical liquid. Also, consider using the 'filter' on mixed magical/mundane gas blends, as they can transform into high-value liquids. Be cautious of directly combining disparate ingredients (magical/mundane) without tool use, as this often leads to negative values.
